<h4 id="what-is-the-crap-of-importance-sampling-">what is the crap of importance sampling ?</h4>
<ol>
  <li>the concept behind this is pretty simple. Do more sampling in important place.</li>
  <li>but how to measure the importance of each sampling point.</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="compared-with-slice-sampling">compared with slice sampling</h4>

<ol>
  <li>importance sampling wasting a lot of time drawing samples that outside of the curve and rejecting it</li>
  <li>slice sampling without any wasting time on points outside the curve</li>
</ol>
